data.description: ***NO FLOOD INSURANCE REQUIRED!!***This home is priced with Value Range Marketing pricing, which means seller will entertain offers within the $199k-$210k range. Your home search is over!!! This beautiful 3BR/2BA contemporary traditional home is inviting, and just says welcome home from the moment you walk in! Nestled within an established neighborhood, the home displays charm & character! Stepping inside the front door, you'll be greeted by a spacious and inviting living area with laminate wood flooring, high vaulted ceilings, a large stone wood-burning fireplace, perfect for those cold winter nights, and skylights that allow plenty of natural lighting to come in. The large family room/den is perfect for family game nights or entertaining a large group of friends. The open-concept kitchen features a pass-thru bar over beautiful granite countertops, looking into the family room!!. This house has a large deck outside the family room/den and an enclosed backyard space that is ideal for outdoor gatherings. Don't miss out on the wonderful opportunity of making this your forever home. Roof is only 8 years old, hot water heater is only 2 years old and A/C unit is only 1 & 1/2 years old, per seller! Schedule your showing today! The home is currently occupied by owner; therefore, please give 24 hour notice to schedule all appointments.***Listing Agent makes no representation to the accuracy of information; therefore, buyer or buyer's agent to verify all pertinent information.
